                    "You know the {@spell druidcraft} cantrip. Starting at 3rd level, you can cast the {@spell disguise self} spell with this trait. Starting at 5th level, you can also cast the {@spell enlarge/reduce} spell with this trait. Once you cast {@spell disguise self} or {@spell enlarge/reduce} with this trait, you can't cast that spell with it again until you finish a long rest. You can also cast either of those spells using any spell slots you have of the appropriate level.",
